#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:4
msgid ""
"Please choose the disk which has the free space required (column Free) to "
"install Debian GNU/Linux. If there's not enough free space, space can be "
"liberated by resizing the FAT partitions (column FreeFat indicates how much "
"space will be freed by resizing the existing FAT partitions)."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, dewiwch y disg sy gyda'r gofod rhydd angenrheidiol (y "
"golofn Rhydd) er mwyn sefydlu GNU/Linux Debian. Os nad oes digon o ofod "
"rhydd, gellir rhyddhau lle gan ailfeintio'r rhaniadau FAT. (Mae'r golofn "
"FatRhydd yn dangos faint o le a rhyddheir gan ailfeintio'r rhaniadau FAT "
"sy'n bodoli.)"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:4
msgid " Device   Model               Size   Free   FreeFAT NbPart"
msgstr " Dyfais   Model               Maint  Rhydd  FreeFAT Rhaniadau"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:4
msgid "${TABLE}"
msgstr "${TABLE}"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../templates:17
msgid "Device to partition:"
msgstr "Y dyfais i'w rhaniadu:"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../templates:17
msgid ""
"No disk was automatically detected.  Please enter the path to the device "
"file for the disk you want to partition."
msgstr ""
"Ni chafodd disg ei ddewis yn awtomatig. Os gwelwch yn dda, rhowch y llwybr "
"at y ffeil dyfais ar gyfer y disg hoffwch rhaniadu."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:24
msgid "Really use the automatic partitioning tool?"
msgstr "Defnyddio'r offeryn rhaniadu awtomatig go iawn?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:24
msgid ""
"This will destroy the partition table on all disks in the machine. REPEAT: "
"THIS WILL WIPE CLEAN ALL HARD DISKS IN THE MACHINE! If you have important "
"data that are not backed up, you may want to stop now in order to do a "
"backup. In that case, you'll have to restart the installation later."
msgstr ""
"Fe fydd hyn yn dinistrio'r tabl rhaniadau ar bob disg yn y peiriant. ETO: FE "
"FYDD HYN YN CLIRIO POB DISGEN GALED YN Y PERIRIANT YN LLWYR! Os mae data "
"pwysig gennych heb gopi wrth gefn, efallai hoffwch erthylu nawr er mwyn creu "
"copi wrth gefn. Yn yr achos hynny, bydd rhaid i chi ailgychwyn y sefydliad "
"yn hwyrach."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "An error occured during the previous operation"
msgstr "Digwyddodd gwall yn ystod y weithred blaenorol"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "You may be able to continue. Here is some more information:"
msgstr "Efallai gallwch fynd ymlaen. Dyma fwy o wybodaeth:"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "${error}"
msgstr "${error}"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid "Automatic partitioning impossible"
msgstr "Mae rhaniadu awtomatig yn amhosib"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid ""
"This version of the autopartitioner cannot handle the partitioning of the "
"selected disk. It may partition only an empty disk or a disk with no more "
"than 2 FAT partitions (and no extended partitions or other non-FAT "
"partitions)."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw fersiwn yma yr awtorhaniadydd yn gallu ymddelio â rhaniadu y disg "
"dewisiedig. Gall rhaniadu dim ond disgiau gwag a disgiau gyda dim mwy na dau "
"rhaniad FAT (a dim rhaniad estynedig neu rhaniadau eraill nid FAT ydynt)."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid ""
"If you want to continue the installation process, switch to the second "
"console (ALT+F2), partition the disk as you like using parted and the other "
"available tools, and then mount all your partitions in /target. /target is "
"the root directory of your new system, so your root partition will be "
"mounted on /target and your /usr partition must be mounted on /target/usr."
msgstr ""
"Os hoffech fynd ymlaen gyda'r broses rhaniadu, ewch at yr ail gonsol (ALT"
"+F2), rhaniadwch y ddisg fel y hoffech gan ddefnyddio parted a'r rhaglenni "
"eraill sydd ar gael, yna clymwch eich holl rhaniadau yn /target. Mae /target "
"yn gyfeiriadur gwraidd y system newydd, felly bydd eich cyfeiriadur gwraidd "
"wedi ei glymu at /target a rhaid bod eich rhaniad /usr wedi ei glymu at /"
"target/usr."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid ""
"You can also consider launching this program again but selecting another "
"disk."
msgstr "Galllwch hefyd geisio lansio'r rhaglen hwn eto ond dewis disg arall."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:58
msgid "Not enough space on disk"
msgstr "Dim digon o le ar y ddisg"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:58
msgid ""
"The autopartitioner makes some assumptions about partition sizes, and "
"because of that it requires at least 3GB of free space. The free space on "
"this disk appears to be below this limit."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r awtorhaniadydd yn cymryd rhai pethau yn ganataol ynghylch meintiau "
"rhaniadau, ac oherwydd hynny mae angen o leiaf 3GB o ofod rhydd. Ymddengys "
"fod y gofod rhydd ar y disg hwn yn llai na'r terfyn yma."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:58
msgid ""
"If you really want to install, you'll have to free some space. You may also "
"launch this program again and select another disk with more free space."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych wir eisiau sefydlu, bydd rhaid i chi rhyddhau mwy o le. Gallwch "
"hefyd lansio'r rhaglen hwn eto a dewis disg arall gyda mwy o le rhydd."

